{"type":"message","id":"a23e9126","parentId":"e0c77081","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:30:43.894Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4e1a2e31dfcb47a4b302a499","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# 修复 Cron 任务执行模式问题\n# 创建时间: 2026-03-07 04:30\n# 问题: nginx-security-daily 和 analyze-openclaw-updates 在错误的模式下执行导致失败\n\nset -e\n\necho \"🔧 Cron 任务执行模式修复脚本\"\necho \"================================\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 检查是否在 workspace 目录\nif [ ! -d \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ 错误: 未找到 workspace 目录\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspace\n\n# 1. 修复 nginx-security-daily (从 main 改为 isolated)\necho \"📋 任务 1: 修复 nginx-security-daily\"\necho \"   问题: 在 main session 执行，需要改为 isolated 模式\"\necho \"\"\n\nTASK_ID=\"defa8238-721d-400a-9786-85f0283b8155\"\nTASK_NAME=\"nginx-security-daily\"\n\n# 检查任务是否存在\nif openclaw cron list | grep -q \"$TASK_ID\"; then\n    echo \"   ✅ 找到任务: $TASK_NAME ($TASK_ID)\"\n    echo \"   当前配置:\"\n    openclaw cron list | grep \"$TASK_ID\" || true\n    echo \"\"\n    \n    # 尝试修改任务配置\n    echo \"   🔄 尝试修改执行模式为 isolated...\"\n    if openclaw cron edit --target isolated \"$TASK_ID\" 2>&1; then\n        echo \"   ✅ 执行模式已更新为 isolated\"\n    else\n        echo \"   ⚠️  自动修改失败，需要手动修改\"\n        echo \"   手动命令: openclaw cron edit --target isolated $TASK_ID\"\n    fi\nelse\n    echo \"   ⚠️  未找到任务: $TASK_NAME\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"---\"\necho \"\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# 修复 Cron 任务执行模式问题\n# 创建时间: 2026-03-07 04:30\n# 问题: nginx-security-daily 和 analyze-openclaw-updates 在错误的模式下执行导致失败\n\nset -e\n\necho \"🔧 Cron 任务执行模式修复脚本\"\necho \"================================\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 检查是否在 workspace 目录\nif [ ! -d \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ 错误: 未找到 workspace 目录\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspace\n\n# 1. 修复 nginx-security-daily (从 main 改为 isolated)\necho \"📋 任务 1: 修复 nginx-security-daily\"\necho \"   问题: 在 main session 执行，需要改为 isolated 模式\"\necho \"\"\n\nTASK_ID=\"defa8238-721d-400a-9786-85f0283b8155\"\nTASK_NAME=\"nginx-security-daily\"\n\n# 检查任务是否存在\nif openclaw cron list | grep -q \"$TASK_ID\"; then\n    echo \"   ✅ 找到任务: $TASK_NAME ($TASK_ID)\"\n    echo \"   当前配置:\"\n    openclaw cron list | grep \"$TASK_ID\" || true\n    echo \"\"\n    \n    # 尝试修改任务配置\n    echo \"   🔄 尝试修改执行模式为 isolated...\"\n    if openclaw cron edit --target isolated \"$TASK_ID\" 2>&1; then\n        echo \"   ✅ 执行模式已更新为 isolated\"\n    else\n        echo \"   ⚠️  自动修改失败，需要手动修改\"\n        echo \"   手动命令: openclaw cron edit --target isolated $TASK_ID\"\n    fi\nelse\n    echo \"   ⚠️  未找到任务: $TASK_NAME\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"---\"\necho \"\"","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772843443893}}
{"type":"message","id":"d23a5682","parentId":"a23e9126","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:30:45.805Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_797ce1571b504a72b79b085b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.21 (9dff8e2) — I can't fix your code taste, but I can fix your build and your backlog.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\n\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\n\nArguments:\n  id                        Job id\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>              Set agent id\n  --announce                Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style)\n  --at <when>               Set one-shot time (ISO) or duration like 20m\n  --best-effort-deliver     Do not fail job if delivery fails\n  --channel <channel>       Delivery channel (last)\n  --clear-agent             Unset agent and use default (default: false)\n  --cron <expr>             Set cron expression\n  --delete-after-run        Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default:\n                            false)\n  --deliver                 Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to\n                            a chat.\n  --description <text>      Set description\n  --disable                 Disable job (default: false)\n  --enable                  Enable job (default: false)\n  --every <duration>        Set interval duration like 10m\n  --exact                   Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0)\n  --expect-final            Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help                Display help for command\n  --keep-after-run          Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1906,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.21 (9dff8e2) — I can't fix your code taste, but I can fix your build and your backlog.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron edit [options] <id>\n\nEdit a cron job (patch fields)\n\nArguments:\n  id                        Job id\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>              Set agent id\n  --announce                Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style)\n  --at <when>               Set one-shot time (ISO) or duration like 20m\n  --best-effort-deliver     Do not fail job if delivery fails\n  --channel <channel>       Delivery channel (last)\n  --clear-agent             Unset agent and use default (default: false)\n  --cron <expr>             Set cron expression\n  --delete-after-run        Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default:\n                            false)\n  --deliver                 Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to\n                            a chat.\n  --description <text>      Set description\n  --disable                 Disable job (default: false)\n  --enable                  Enable job (default: false)\n  --every <duration>        Set interval duration like 10m\n  --exact                   Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0)\n  --expect-final            Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help                Display help for command\n  --keep-after-run          Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772843445803}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea9cfc43","parentId":"d23a5682","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:30:57.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了问题：\n1. 上次创建的脚本使用了 `--target` 参数，但实际上应该是 `--agent` 参数\n2. nginx-security-daily 的配置显示: `main main`（target=main, agent=main）\n3. analyze-openclaw-updates 的配置显示: `isolated default`（target=isolated, agent=default）\n\n所以问题是：\n- nginx-security-daily: 需要将 agent 从 main 改为 default（或其他合适的 agent）\n- analyze-openclaw-updates: 已经是 isolated 模式，但仍然失败，说明是其他问题\n\n让我继续查看更多帮助信息，了解如何正确修改。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e6f4caa2d82645118f0ce8f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron edit --help 2>&1 | grep -A 5 -B 5 \"agent\\|target\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64b65dc0b18c457f834ab9c8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron runs defa8238-721d-400a-9786-85f0283b8155 2>&1 | tail -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8a183194c4f34b0191875994","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron runs 6224b803-66d9-4ede-9b97-b4b88052ea7f 2>&1 | tail -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1196,"output":267,"cacheRead":129216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772843445805}}
